text: Marilou Cayco is a Filipina politician from Batanes island in the Philippines, and currently the Governor of Batanes. She has been elected two terms as a Governor of Batanes. She first won election to Governor in 2016 and was re- elected in 2019. ==References== ==External links== *Province of Batanes Official Website Category:Living people Category:21st-century Filipino politicians Category:Governors of Batanes Category:Liberal Party (Philippines) politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
